Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Intro}Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:28.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:02:59.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:49.10,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:38.06,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:08.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Outro}Outro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I say something amazing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As for how amazing it is-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and say it. Chop-chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, embarking on that "first step"\Ntakes courage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The... Dharma... Doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fell down. Like when you play that game?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking about something on\Na much larger scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The human race that first ate natto must've had\Nsome ridiculous amount of courage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff's practically rotten beans, you know.\NNormally, would you even think of eating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The first person who ate durian\Nmust've been crazy too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, someone like Kusaya!\NI mean, her name's Kusaya for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like beyond imposing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it on top of piping hot rice! Skip the hot mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,More! More of the smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's irresistible! This stench!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live Princess Kusaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:49.65,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With that being said, I have decided\Nto embark on my first step too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Tanaka, will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,at this time, gather up my courage and...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat a loaf of bread that's\Nthree years past its expiration date!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead and eat it!\NAnd then get an upset stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the mold. It's like a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Isn't it amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me for calling out to you so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on uniform and ribbon colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that you're 1st-years at Saijo,\Nso I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well that's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you know of a person named Hisui Kujyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kujyo...? I've heard of that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she's in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her younger twin sister, and my name is Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this is a rather intrusive request but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you become friends with my big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, my big sister tends to\Nrefuse to go to school and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen her much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we entered school, I can probably\Ncount on my fingers how often she's shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she won't meet the number of attendance days required,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and she'll probably be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's why you're asking us to be friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister has been a little different since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanta-kun, what should we play today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with picture books and TV programs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the heartful stories\Nthat normal kids delight in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.83,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hamburgers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.41,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Not what you wanna eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.17,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Jeez Wanta-kun, you're such a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the kid that preferred\Nthe kind of grotesque ones
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,where blood would spray out everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she grew up just the same way,\Nand rather than real living human beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,my big sister took an interest in\Nzombies and occult stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gradually, she ended up\Nspooking everyone around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister isnâ€™t good at communicating for herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and even when asked why she's\Nnot inclined to head to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd only say, "because I don't have friends"\Nor "because it's boring" or stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I remember! It's Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the nickname I gave to Hisui Kujyo awhile back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, that fits my big sister perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're totally fine with being her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Uh, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A-are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Never hesitate to do what's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone ahead and summoned\Nmy big sister here right away...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Younger sister, you sure act fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the older sister, the younger sister\Nis rather aggressive, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That's why I feel responsible and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I took away all of my big sister's\Ncommunication abilities and normal sensibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said that maybe my big sister\Nwas left with only remnant trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were some terrible things\Nthat were said to you, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's left is for my big sister to come-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, they're people from the same class as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you tricked me, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I came as fast as I could, because you said\Nthat you'd found a bipedal tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here, seriously believing that?!\NYou've got a pure heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there. I'm the bipedal walking tsuchinoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna complicate things, so you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey wait! Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.08,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Lemme go! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:48.74,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'm going home! Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you wanna go home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when everyone has kindly said\Nthat they'll be your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's for real!\NLet's go tsuchinoko searching together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you gotta come to school starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please let me think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so she said yesterday, but...\NIs she gonna come? That Majo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! If she doesn't come,\Nthen I'll use this thing I took at the river recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll summon her with this photo of Tamassie,\Nthe unidentified mysterious animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're gonna take a trick photo,\Nthen put a little more effort into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she came!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,G-good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... This is a thank you for\Nhaving made your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I pulled an all-nighter and made these last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A friendship bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I put in a wish that you would be\Nfriendly to me forever and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I put my heart and soul into braiding them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, this material is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,B-by any chance, is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my hair but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's freaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called? That yummy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing where a cut is made around the belly\Nand then stuffed with rice and stewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-when you say a cut is made in\Nthe abdomen and rice put in and it's stewed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about torture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to get your hopes up,\Nbut she's talking about cooking, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,C-cooking?! M-my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you were talking about human-eaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to link things directly to that stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiight! I'll take on whatever you dish out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now! It's samgyetang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Samgyetang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aw... I'm kinda getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I do have salicylic acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's that? Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you drink it straight up, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Um... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to join the conversations at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! I forgot what Kohaku had told me yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for friendship bracelets for\NBaka-san and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Big Sis, why did you have to go\Nand be so you, Big Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want your friends to dislike you,\Nthen you can't talk one-sidedly about the occult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but... Then, what do I talk about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Funny!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cute!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you reuse these three for different occasions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then for the time being, you'll be able to\Nconverse with high school girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right." "Funny." "Cute."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! I haven't seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I got suddenly talked to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,State your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,R...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, her name is "Right."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,, Hey you, why haven't you come to school more often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of attribute are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,F...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know, then I'll tell you, but you\Nshouldn't joke around too much towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how I look, I am the chosen one\Nwith the hidden power of the dragon, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As it were, I am a presence to be feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally messing with me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you bastard! There'll probably come a time\Nwhen we'll fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,F-fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been disliked without warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat kalbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do have carbinoxamine maleate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop checking every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's most important, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine if you mix it in with the barbeque sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Why Kujyo, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good you came to school. Sensei is happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Paranormal photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kujyo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I went and gathered all the printouts\Nthat were passed out while you were absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the materials from\Nworld history, and these-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right thats...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Am I interpreting it correctly with "right that" \Nas the demonstrative pronouns, and "s" as the ending suffix?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it an acronym?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she taking the first letters of Reimen,\NThe napolitan, and Somen noodles,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to make "Right ThatS"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't talk at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, I'm not getting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.46,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be afraid. Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.15,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'll bite ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.50,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you bite me, just get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.20,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Enough! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.37,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Before you go home, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.27,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely impossible for me to have that kind of friendly conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm not cut out for school after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We take the train, so it'll only be part-way, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,F... F... F... F...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You don't have to worry about that.\NYou can say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me. I open my mouth and\NI say stuff like poop, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You mend your ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,P-people... And all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, I'm scared of being disliked and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I get so caught up just thinking about that and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just totally can't do it well and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I shut myself away in my own little world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's safe if I stay there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that way, I can avoid\Nbeing disliked and getting hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But... The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to be liked by every single person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just make sure to cherish\Nthe people who do understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop with this gloomy mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna make me itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbinoxamine maleate also works well on itchiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?! Kalbi does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! She's not talking about kalbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should just make sure to cherish\Nthe people who do understand you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to do it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, let's go see a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,D-do we really have to see something like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough that it's a holiday\Nand there's a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like a romance movie is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's setting the bar too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not high!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, you've gotta know more\Nabout the trends of normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be able to have fun conversations\Nwith your friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go buy something to drink,\Nso wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same class...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I believe Baka-san said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Tanaka said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.70,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Loli-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in the same class as Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Twins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kohaku, her younger twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you here to see "Love with you" as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it. I mean, yes, that's so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not as if I came to see this movie\Nbecause I wanted to, or anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan, you may be able to\Nlearn about the adult world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,by watching stuff like romance movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An acquaintance strongly recommended me to, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I totally don't like these kind of chick flicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both so difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.72,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I... I don't want Ryuji to have you after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.46,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hey...! Where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.79,Alternate,,0,0,0,,You've also got your girlfriend Lisa, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.86,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I can't help it, now that I've realized that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:46.25,Alternate,,0,0,0,,the one who's really important to me, is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.18,Alternate,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:50.35,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, when I saw the manganji chili pepper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.40,Alternate,,0,0,0,,in your bento lunch box, it made me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.80,Alternate,,0,0,0,,That I can't lie to myself, about my feelings anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.99,Alternate,,0,0,0,,But, that was Lisa's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.01,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Do you know the manganji chili pepper's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.01,Alternate,,0,0,0,,flower meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.58,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I don't know something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.93,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.07,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's "I won't let you go, for the rest of your life!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! So cool! This makes my heart skip a beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This man... That he's forcing a woman who has\Na significant other to go with him is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he has his own significant other too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These bastards...!\NThey're skipping school like it's no big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Their parents would cry if they ever found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of messy romance is normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are scary after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not even going out yet,\Nbut they're holding hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like super delinquents...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.09,Alternate,,0,0,0,,No! If someone saw us like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.83,Alternate,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, then stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw... How boring that not a\Nsingle drop of blood is being spilt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish someone would get killed soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A maiden who's not even married yet is k-kis...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if a child sees something like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.62,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I love you, Erika...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.89,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.62,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'll never let you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:21.43,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Even if the manganji chili pepper's flower dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.99,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was entertaining!\NIt was a tearjerker at the end, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of thinking that as long as\Nyou and your own are happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then you don't care about other people is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,horrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like the movie was\Njam-packed with people's egoism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The serious main character was corrupted by\Na delinquent and steadily became irresponsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a movie that should've gotten a R12 rating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you go to the movie theater by yourself a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like so mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess. There' no one of\Nthe same age that I can casually invite, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to high school girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just inviting them might make them say\Nsomething like "die!", so it's s-scary, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it seems like... Maybe Loli-san understands me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.95,Alternate,,0,0,0,,What's with that?\NMajo, it's like you don't stand out at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.43,Alternate,,0,0,0,,but outside from it,\Nyou're kinda different than what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Um, Loli-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be other chances to talk to her. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Baka-san, Wota-san, Robo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up, Majo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I came up with just a little game, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.04,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a "ways of dying Amida lottery."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you pick the number you want,\Nand it'll forecast the way you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to explain it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We more or less have an idea of what it entails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come up with another icky game again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd jump at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, number three for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Three it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... It goes here and then this way and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be "beaten to death."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo, you got just the right blunt weapon with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the efficient thing would be\Nthe corners of the desk or chair-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting killed, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Wota, you do it next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you can die in the most pitiful way possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's just plain old bad-mouthing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this only has pitiful ways to die, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:25.42,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Target: Kujyo. Codename "Majo", spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though that one hardly came to school at all,\Nshe all of a sudden appeared a few days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and before anyone noticed, she'd integrated\Nherself with Baka and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.30,Alternate,,0,0,0,,How about adding skewered,\Nskinned alive, or the Brazen Bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:41.55,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's where a person is put inside a hollow\Nbrass bull and fire is put under it to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.23,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Those are all executions or torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.64,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:45.96,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Gah! I'm gonna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger level three.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll continue tracking from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayday, mayday. Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of danger levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're doing there puts you\Nat the final stage, Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the girl from Class 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute. She looks like an elementary student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me, you airheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to talk to her again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just make sure to cherish\Nthe people who do understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be too difficult after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you're... Yamai-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just an alias, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo, or whatever your name is.\NYou're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have been able to deceive the others,\Nbut it won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay... Yamai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,your underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:17:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I was showing it on purpose,\Nto throw you off guard, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,H-h-how's that?! You got thrown off guard, right?!\NAnd it got you rattled, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not tell anyone\Nwhat you just saw. You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,M-m-more importantly,\Nhurry up and give up your secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! E-even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret... Secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if you don't tell normal people\Nthat you like this kind of stuff, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I like seeing people's blood,\Nmore than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,E-especially, I can't get enough of the sight of blood,\Nvigorously gushing out from the carotid artery...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and of course, I also love when the\Ninternal organs pulsate after being dragged out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...far more than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you two over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got something to do, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take care of the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do we have to do\Nyour share of things...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I've got this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with their cleanup altogether, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna clean both of them up altogether?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleanup done...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you guys, hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's no need to go that far, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to do it by yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... You know... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.89,Alternate,,0,0,0,,So kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, then since things are more or less done,\Nshall we also just finish up by throwing out the trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah, sure! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go get the dustpan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You dropped some...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamai-san! Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I already took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The trash?! With your bare hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw out the trash too,\Nso you go ahead and head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What? B-but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's fine. It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to Majo...\NWhen it comes to Majo, I must not piss her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get to say thank you to Yamai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but she sure is a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job with the cleaning duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry, so let's eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Loli-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Choco-bat's yummy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.17,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I-I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... n-next time... t-together... a-a-a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go see one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the next one will be like a heartwarming story\Nwith no delinquents showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm sorry! That's a no, right?\NWe haven't even gotten close yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna go hang myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You better invite me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo's Choco Bat is a home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's true! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've seen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky! You're so lucky! I wanna home run too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.05,Alternate,,0,0,0,,You just keep striking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,About today, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,will probably never forget the taste of the\NChoco Bat that I ate together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop preserving anything\Nand everything in formalin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably for the rest of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of movie really does\Nfeel heartwarming after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo and Loli are probably enjoying\Nthe movie about now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Robo, what're you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried to make one for Baka as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A reincarnation Amida lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of those about what you'll become\Nif you get reborn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I pick number five!
